Name: Circle of Wind
Desc: Calls forth a twister that pushes enemies backward with damage. Some monsters have a resistance to the attack and cannot be pulled.

H.Old:
MP Cost: 40. Attacks 6 enemies at 108% damage 5 times and pushes them away.
After using a Mir Skill, casting Circle of Wind while Circle of Mana is active or while laying down, activates a Fusion Skill instead, but costs 3x more MP.
H.New:
MP Cost: 40. Attacks up to 6 enemies at 108% Damage 5 times and pushes them away.
